00:01:08.220 --> 00:01:10.820
(On the full moon night, man and deity
combine to make a Twin-soul Contract.)

00:01:12.040 --> 00:01:13.200
(On the full moon night,)

00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:15.840
(human and deity combine
to make a Twin-soul Contract.)

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:19.600
(I am as lowly as grass.)

00:01:21.120 --> 00:01:22.800
(But no prairie fire
can destroy the grass,)

00:01:23.760 --> 00:01:25.520
(it shoots up again
when the spring breeze blows.)

00:01:29.240 --> 00:01:31.240
Please make a pact with me.

00:01:32.040 --> 00:01:33.240
Make a pact with you?

00:01:34.240 --> 00:01:35.160
You don't deserve it.

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:36.520
I will do anything

00:01:36.520 --> 00:01:37.560
you say.

00:01:37.960 --> 00:01:38.800
Please.

00:01:39.880 --> 00:01:40.680
Please?

00:01:56.440 --> 00:01:57.800
Don't leave this place.

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:01.680
I'll find a way to remove
the Xuanzhu Jade from your body.

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:08.160
(Legend has it)

00:02:08.520 --> 00:02:09.960
(that the Divine Beast Phoenix)

00:02:09.960 --> 00:02:11.520
(loses his mind
on the night of the full moon.)

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:14.040
(At that time,
his power is at his weakest.)

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:15.920
(After tonight,)

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:17.520
(I'll lose my chance.)

00:02:56.880 --> 00:02:57.880
What are you up to?

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:11.920
(Why is there no reaction?)

00:03:13.120 --> 00:03:14.720
(How can we form a pact?)

00:03:19.080 --> 00:03:19.920
What are you doing?

00:03:21.040 --> 00:03:21.920
Stay back.

00:03:33.800 --> 00:03:34.400
(No.)

00:03:34.720 --> 00:03:35.560
(He's lost his mind.)

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:36.600
(I must control him.)

00:03:40.520 --> 00:03:41.680
Make a pact with me.

00:03:42.240 --> 00:03:43.520
I'll give you

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:45.320
whatever you want.

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:53.760
(A pact?)

00:03:54.600 --> 00:03:55.800
(Make a pact with her,)

00:03:57.120 --> 00:03:58.320
(and save the clan.)

00:04:02.840 --> 00:04:04.000
Blood?

00:04:15.720 --> 00:04:16.600
Kill her.

00:04:17.880 --> 00:04:19.640
Drain her blood.

00:04:22.080 --> 00:04:23.000
(What's wrong with him?)

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:24.840
(Kill her.)

00:04:25.840 --> 00:04:26.680
(Kill her!)

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:33.000
(No matter what the price is,)

00:04:33.640 --> 00:04:35.480
(I must avenge the Mu family.)

00:04:42.960 --> 00:04:44.080
(What's going on?)

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:46.920
(How can this woman)

00:04:48.360 --> 00:04:50.120
(seal my power?)

00:05:11.260 --> 00:05:13.020
(The contract is sealed.
Twin cultivation took place)

00:05:13.030 --> 00:05:16.020
(on the full moon night.
Whoever betrays will suffer backlash.)

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:48.080
A union between a human and a deity,

00:05:48.880 --> 00:05:50.120
Twin-soul Contract.

00:05:51.680 --> 00:05:53.200
You can no longer harm me.

00:05:54.640 --> 00:05:55.240
Do you understand,

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:58.240
Lord Divine Beast?

00:06:20.180 --> 00:06:22.820
(Ji Yuchen, Ji Xinwu, Ji Yuanying)

00:06:43.240 --> 00:06:44.040
(What is this?)

00:06:49.640 --> 00:06:53.480
How dare you attack me
while I was meditating?

00:06:55.200 --> 00:06:56.920
I'm just a lowly human.

00:06:57.520 --> 00:06:59.320
How could I possibly
take advantage of your weakness?

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:01.720
It was just a night
full of uncertainties.

00:07:02.440 --> 00:07:03.760
A lonely man and woman

00:07:04.320 --> 00:07:05.560
who came together willingly.

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:06.240
Shut it.

00:07:07.440 --> 00:07:08.400
You're courting death.

00:07:12.100 --> 00:07:13.440
(Ji)

00:07:13.440 --> 00:07:17.200
You should carve one for yourself.

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:22.800
Soon.

00:07:23.840 --> 00:07:28.520
But they'll have to die one by one
by my hand first.

00:07:29.280 --> 00:07:32.600
I decide when that will be.

00:07:48.840 --> 00:07:50.080
I won.

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:52.880
From now on, we're bound
by the Twin-soul Contract.

00:07:52.880 --> 00:07:56.800
Hurting me is hurting yourself.
We share the pain.

00:07:56.920 --> 00:07:57.680
So what?

00:07:58.280 --> 00:07:59.920
I can't feel pain like humans do.

00:08:00.520 --> 00:08:01.400
How shameless.

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:05.240
Humans will do anything
to get what they want.

00:08:15.250 --> 00:08:16.680
We are both bound
by the Twin-soul Contract.

00:08:17.440 --> 00:08:18.680
You can't hurt me.

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:26.200
(Kill her.)

00:08:27.200 --> 00:08:28.560
(Drain her blood,)

00:08:28.680 --> 00:08:30.080
(and the Xuanzhu Jade can be destroyed.)

00:08:33.320 --> 00:08:34.560
No.

00:08:35.240 --> 00:08:37.760
I need the Xuanzhu Jade
to save the Scarlet Flame Clan.

00:08:38.400 --> 00:08:39.400
(What's wrong with him again?)

00:08:41.160 --> 00:08:43.840
(You're the one who caused them
to be frozen in ice.)

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:45.760
(Even if you save them,)

00:08:45.840 --> 00:08:47.080
(will they forgive you?)

00:08:48.280 --> 00:08:50.560
(If it wasn't for you
to hold my evil soul,)

00:08:50.560 --> 00:08:52.240
(you would've frozen to death too.)

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:54.600
(You should destroy the Xuanzhu Jade)

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:57.160
(and ascend with me.)

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:08.800
(Chi Yu,)

00:09:09.480 --> 00:09:10.960
(you fool.)

00:09:12.040 --> 00:09:14.000
(You actually made a pact
with a mortal.)

00:09:19.040 --> 00:09:20.080
I told you.

00:09:20.360 --> 00:09:21.680
You can't kill me

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:25.720
because of the Twin-soul Contract.

00:09:39.600 --> 00:09:40.920
Lowly human.

00:10:03.240 --> 00:10:04.840
Do you have no family left either?

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:13.680
Where are you taking me?

00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:10.440
Can my blood melt the ice?

00:11:54.920 --> 00:11:56.080
(Why is there no effect?)

00:12:00.200 --> 00:12:01.040
It's useless.

00:12:06.840 --> 00:12:07.640
Get out.

00:12:08.560 --> 00:12:10.160
You shouldn't be here.

00:12:25.920 --> 00:12:26.680
Why did they...

00:12:26.680 --> 00:12:27.360
Scram.

00:12:27.760 --> 00:12:29.160
Don't make me repeat myself.

00:12:45.400 --> 00:12:46.480
Let's cooperate.

00:12:46.680 --> 00:12:48.040
You help me take revenge,

00:12:48.200 --> 00:12:49.640
and I'll sacrifice myself willingly.

00:12:50.240 --> 00:12:51.040
Three months from now,

00:12:51.040 --> 00:12:52.040
on the Day of Xihe,

00:12:52.240 --> 00:12:53.480
return the Xuanzhu Jade to its place

00:12:53.520 --> 00:12:54.760
and save your clan.

00:12:57.840 --> 00:13:00.960
If not, the Scarlet Flame Clan
will suffer in the ice forever.

00:13:04.360 --> 00:13:05.360
Are you threatening me?

00:13:07.840 --> 00:13:09.880
You're the high and mighty
Phoenix Divine Beast.

00:13:09.960 --> 00:13:11.880
Don't you even
have the courage for that?

00:13:12.840 --> 00:13:14.560
Does repenting in front of your people

00:13:14.640 --> 00:13:16.040
solve the problem?

00:13:17.360 --> 00:13:19.240
I will not cooperate with anyone again.

00:13:19.920 --> 00:13:23.080
I'm warning you, keep your place,

00:13:23.840 --> 00:13:25.720
and you may live a little longer.

00:13:28.920 --> 00:13:31.840
(Back then, I trusted the Silver Fox
Clan and worked with them,)

00:13:32.640 --> 00:13:34.160
(that's why the Xuanzhu Jade
fell out of place.)

00:13:35.800 --> 00:13:37.480
(I will never repeat that mistake.)

00:13:43.380 --> 00:13:45.940
=Twin Fates=
=End of Episode 2=

